## [2.0.0] - 2022-12-05
### WARNING
This release has breaking changes to the database.
If you were using Clu (the old name) v1.x
See this document for upgrade instructions.

https://github.com/corporate-runaways/TooLoo/blob/main/docs/1_to_2_upgrade.md


### Added
* Added an optional read-only REST API
* Added support for asciicasts (Asciinema)
* Added support for tags
* Can now export to Markdown
* Can now output JSON
* Added the ability to ingest all .toml files in a directory

### Changed
* New tables & columns in the db
* DB now lives under XDG_DATA_HOME
* Default Templates now suffixed with .toml instead of .meta.toml
* Changed license to AGPL



## [1.0.1] - 2022-10-05
### Fixed
*  changed README markup format

## [1.0.0] - 2022-10-05
